## Common examples in bodybuilding names

| Stored in master | Unicode | Plain ASCII |
|-----------------|---------|-------------|
| `Pen~a` | Peña | Pena |
| `Lun~ez` | Luñez | Lunez |
| `Alve's` | Alvés | Alves |
| `Rodri'guez` | Rodríguez | Rodriguez |
| `Fe'lix` | Félix | Felix |
| `Mo'ricz` | Móricz | Moricz |
| `Gu:nter` | Günter | Gunter |
| `Cze's` | Cześ | Czes |
| `S^tefan` | Štefan | Stefan |
